3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4693-4
00:33:52.229 --> 00:33:53.272
<v Siim Vene>õige vastus on 3.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4697-0
00:33:54.432 --> 00:33:56.542
<v Siim Vene>Ja see 3 ei ole.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4727-0
00:33:57.302 --> 00:34:00.696
<v Siim Vene>Juhuslik number et kas keegi oskab 2.
