3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4734-0
00:34:15.482 --> 00:34:16.772
<v Siim Vene>Nogard sul on käsi püsti.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4742-0
00:34:17.562 --> 00:34:19.082
<v Karl Kevin Piks&#246;&#246;t>Et ikka veel tabelit hoida?</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4780-0
00:34:20.882 --> 00:34:25.643
<v Siim Vene>Vot ütleme, et suund on.
