3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/4987-7
00:35:51.795 --> 00:35:54.792
<v Siim Vene>erinevates siis nii öelda nendes klastri
õlgades.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5023-0
00:35:55.602 --> 00:35:58.771
<v Siim Vene>Ehk siis see,
