3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5038-1
00:36:12.275 --> 00:36:13.132
<v Siim Vene>mitme lokk atsiooni.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5064-0
00:36:17.282 --> 00:36:21.278
<v Siim Vene>Ja noh, kui te näete,
