3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5099-2
00:36:42.831 --> 00:36:43.452
<v Siim Vene>ehitamist.</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5187-0
00:36:44.282 --> 00:36:48.918
<v Siim Vene>Ja millegipärast on sinna nagu
