3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5387-0
00:38:38.962 --> 00:38:42.702
<v Siim Vene>Siis hoonetest,
kuhu on siis sisse rammitud väga palju</v>

3afee78e-953f-4002-834b-f0fbf4d0755d/5387-1
00:38:42.702 --> 00:38:46.034
<v Siim Vene>arvutustehnikat selleks,
